{"tid":1499751,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國外交部更新對中國的旅遊警示","createTime":"2019-08-24T00:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T02:36:30.000Z","uid":34612,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5012c2628ff303efd734d07972f4fa3564fb932f","tid":1499751,"uid":34612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:04:00.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】英國外交部更新對中國的旅遊警示。<br />\n<br />\n英國外交部網站指出，香港有持續示威和集會後，有報道指，內地當局在連接香港的邊境加強檢查，包括檢查旅客的個人電子設備。英方同時呼籲旅客，要注意內地跟香港的拘留和起訴程序是有分別。"},{"pid":"08b1c1d9a38887f39cc7151fdafdef8bcc2fa88c","tid":1499751,"uid":27670,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:10:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">英方同時呼籲旅客，要注意內地跟香港的拘留和起訴程序是有分別。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e56a1ae230546ad81ecf06d2c9b714216c13367","tid":1499751,"uid":64191,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:10:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/foreign-travel-advice/hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fforeign-travel-advice%2Fhong-kong&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6rc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=963eb870\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/foreign-travel-advice/hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\nIn light of ongoing protests and demonstrations in Hong Kong, there are reports of greater scrutiny from mainland authorities at border crossings between the mainland and Hong Kong. This includes reports that travellers&rsquo; electronic devices have been checked at border crossings.<span style=\"color: red;\"> You should be aware that the thresholds for detention and prosecution in China differ from those in Hong Kong.</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dbe012394ce4c3